sequenceDiagram
    actor "User Browser" as UserBrowser
    participant "Frontend SPA" as FrontendSPA

    activate FrontendSPA
    UserBrowser->>FrontendSPA: 1. 1. Clicks help icon (?) or focuses and presses 'Enter'
    FrontendSPA->>FrontendSPA: 2. 2. handleOpen(): Updates component state to show popover
    FrontendSPA-->>FrontendSPA: State updated: { isOpen: true }
    FrontendSPA->>FrontendSPA: 2.1. 2.1. Looks up help content by ID from local store
    FrontendSPA-->>FrontendSPA: { title, description, learnMoreUrl }
    FrontendSPA->>UserBrowser: 3. 3. Renders <Popover.Content> with help text and displays it
    UserBrowser->>FrontendSPA: 4. 4. Clicks 'Learn More' link
    FrontendSPA->>UserBrowser: 5. 5. Opens knowledge base URL in a new tab
    UserBrowser->>FrontendSPA: 6. 6. Clicks outside popover or presses 'Escape' key
    FrontendSPA->>FrontendSPA: 7. 7. handleClose(): Updates component state to hide popover
    FrontendSPA-->>FrontendSPA: State updated: { isOpen: false }
    FrontendSPA->>UserBrowser: 8. 8. Removes popover from the DOM

